						               													<description>H&amp;amp;S GAMES presents Platoon Leader, an Infantry based WW2 hex and counter game with semi-solitaire engine and optional German AI. It's 1944: You have dropped behind German lines and must use your platoon leaders to command squads through various missions. Platoon Leader is a non-card driven, non combat results table system that utilizes sectors and zones to regulate possible German activation.  Game idiosyncrasies include: Suppression, reaction and a high level of unpredictability which ensures high replayability.  Includes an introductory scenario, 2 full blown scenarios and a zombie variant. Comes with a single map and counters which must be cut and mounted.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
